Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-shacrypt
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-shacrypt
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Generate SHA256-CRYPT and SHA512-CRYPT password hashes in PostgreSQL PGVERSION
  A PostgreSQL extension to generate SHA256-CRYPT and SHA512-CRYPT password hashes.
  See https://www.akkadia.org/drepper/SHA-crypt.txt for the specification and upstream code by Ulrich Drepper.
